{"tid":2185713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國王室恢復詩妮娜王妃稱號","createTime":"2020-09-02T12:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T13:01:49.000Z","uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55f0036070ab7f2c843c65db1a91d6a58ea1dd5c","tid":2185713,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】泰國王室宣布恢復王妃詩妮娜的所有頭銜。<br />\n<br />\n泰國王室指，詩妮娜已在上月29日恢復王妃稱號，又指詩妮娜未有犯下過錯，王室紀錄不應顯示詩妮娜的稱號曾遭褫奪。<br />\n<br />\n35歲的詩妮娜去年七月獲泰王哇集拉隆功封為王妃，是泰國王室近一個世紀以來首次納妃，但詩妮娜在去年十月被指不服從哇集拉隆功，及試圖令自己與王后素提達平起平坐，對泰王構成不敬，詩妮娜所有軍銜和稱號當時遭到褫奪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404094&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404094%26home%3D1&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=68453a1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404094%26home%3D1&h=cb99465b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404094&amp;home=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國宮心計 王室撤銷王妃詩妮娜所有銜頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1667890/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1667890/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1b5ba98facaa340d7238efbde8d354c697b0c58c","tid":2185713,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef3506ae32e8d9896f32e9b85e3ff9d3437804a","tid":2185713,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:55:44.000Z","msg":"白龍王收皮後哩個打靶仔就是旦啦"},{"pid":"30fb3bf6add0ab5ae039098683e98fbe1d2a0c28","tid":2185713,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"